        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lazy_Lake%2C_Florida"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "The village’s only road, Lazy Lane, circles the lake and connects all homes in the enclave.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        24
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lazy_Lake%2C_Florida"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "Founded by Lindfors, Ratliff, and architect Clinton Gamble, Lazy Lake started with just 13 homes on 13 acres.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        5,
        6
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia",
