      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lazy_Lake%2C_Florida"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "Lazy Lake is the smallest incorporated municipality in Broward County by area.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        17
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lazy_Lake%2C_Florida"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "The village sits entirely within the borders of Wilton Manors, making it a landlocked enclave.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
